gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "All right, {PLAYER}{KUN}, the time has\n"
	.string "come.\p"
	.string "Your very own tale of grand\n"
	.string "adventure is about to unfold.\p"
	.string "On your journey, you will meet\n"
	.string "countless Pokémon and People.\p"
	.string "I'm sure that along the way you\n"
	.string "will discover many things, perhaps\l"
	.string "even something about yourself.\p"
	.string "Now, go on, leap into the world of\n"
	.string "Pokémon.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReadyPt::
	.string "Muito bem, {PLAYER}{KUN}, chegou a\n"
	.string "hora.\p"
	.string "Sua própria história de uma grande\n"
	.string "aventura está prestes a começar.\p"
	.string "Em sua jornada, você encontrará\n"
	.string "inúmeros Pokémon e pessoas.\p"
	.string "Tenho certeza de que, no caminho,\n"
	.string "você descobrirá muitas coisas,\l"
	.string "talvez até algo sobre si mesmo.\p"
	.string "Agora vá, mergulhe no mundo dos\n"
	.string "Pokémon.\p"
	.string "$"
	
